  <steps>
    <step num="0">In a bowl, combine the rice, water, and olive oil. </step>
    <step num="1">Stir, then microwave, covered, for 6-8 minutes until the rice is fully cooked. </step>
    <step num="2">Carefully remove the lid, then add black beans, tomatoes, salt, and pepper. Stir to combine. </step>
    <step num="3">Top with avocado and cilantro if desired. </step>
    <step num="4">Enjoy! </step>
